snippet.title: Crashy Cats Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
OUT ON ANDROID. FREE! https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ElectricTurtle.CatCrash

Crash your way through rooms, make a mess and destroy priceless collectibles and expensive electronics.
Crashy Cats is a cat rampage runner where you run, jump, bounce and fly your way through endless levels, knocking over as much stuff as possible!

Follow us on Twitter @CrashyCats: https://twitter.com/crashycats
